commitResults.messageTitle: Update Fee class to be abstract
commitResults.messageBody:
Fee class is instantiable.

Preventing instantiation of Fee class improves the principle
of abstraction.

To prevent instantiation of Fee class, lets:
- Change Fee class to abstract class
- Update FeeTest class to be able to test the abstract class
